author: kalle
msg: 1. Automatic growing capacity of the hashtable.
Increased the capacity with factor 1.7 when the the key posting space use at least 20%
of the available space in the key postings file.
2. Read methods of key postings compares using keyhash before unmarshalling key.
A fairly obvious way to save clock ticks when iterating though large key posting lists
that are associated with the same hash posting.
